{"tid":1095274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子麥記門外中伏 遭4兇徒木棍打傷","createTime":"2019-04-07T02:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T02:44:21.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cbade6469d5d55b6d049323ddd2b6f2ae82a18ef","tid":1095274,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T02:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HM90ddM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHM90ddM.png&h=6a9340c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mRnMTdN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmRnMTdN.png&h=2b0a0c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現場遺下一支折斷木棍。潘志能攝<br />\n<br />\n油塘油麗邨商場麥當勞快餐店門外，早上6時許，四名持木棍兇徒，向一名男子襲擊，他頭手腳受傷，兇徒傷人四散。救護員到場將傷者送院，警方調查案件追緝兇徒下落。"},{"pid":"5c166cd8be8876413e0766c52e9c76aea7dad8f6","tid":1095274,"uid":180184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T02:36:13.000Z","msg":"大本型? 警察個封鎖線會唔會太矮? 阿婆都跳得過喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3298c66792eabfdc5970754ac40d14868f1325e5","tid":1095274,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T02:44:21.000Z","msg":"阿sir做野唔洗你教"}]}